ğŸ” Testing Your Changes

Before submitting a PR:

Load /

Complete onboarding once

Click into a video tile

Open VIA Ribbon

Toggle Investigate Panel

Check browser console for:

SESSION_START

PAGE_VIEW

CTA_CLICK

Investigate events

Ensure no unexpected console errors

ğŸ¯ Pull Request Requirements

Every PR must:

Include a clear title and summary

Describe why the change is needed

Confirm that the preview loads and runs end-to-end

Include screenshots for UI updates

Tag any files altered in /events or the event spine

PRs changing the event system must include:

Before/After event examples

Updated event documentation

Confirmation that event shape remains canonical

âŒ What Not to Do

Do not add any backend code

Do not introduce database calls

Do not modify VIA behavior beyond the mocked scope

Do not rename directories without approval

Do not merge without review

ğŸ§© Design Consistency Rules

Always use existing button and layout classes

Maintain spacing/padding patterns already in styles/

Do not introduce new color tokens unless approved

Follow responsive behaviors defined in existing components

ğŸ—³ Decision-Making Authority

