ğŸ“ Code Standards
JavaScript / React

Use functional components

Use hooks (no class components)

Avoid large components â€” split into smaller parts

Keep imports clean and sorted

Keep business logic out of UI components

Events

Always use EVENT_TYPES.

Always use logEvent().

Never hardcode event type strings inline.

